Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.47,0:21:34.27,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}It's been so long since we left our home behind
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.31,0:21:40.52,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Drifting on the Milky Way almost every single day
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.53,0:21:43.99,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Where am I supposed to go ?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.57,0:21:47.07,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}What're we really looking for ?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.41,0:21:52.16,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Stumbling in the darkness, cold and lost
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.25,0:21:59.04,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}But a ray of hope still exists in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.83,0:22:04.55,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Rain or shine, always chase the dream
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.59,0:22:08.68,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Someday, we'll fly across the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.89,0:22:12.14,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Never fearing anything
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.31,0:22:16.94,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}We'll promise that"we'll go on ! "
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.06,0:22:21.11,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Even if you're against the wind,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.23,0:22:22.61,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Never stop !
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.82,0:22:24.36,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Don't look back !
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.48,0:22:29.78,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}We'll one day rise above it all (never give up)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.82,0:22:33.62,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Who cares if the going's tough
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.70,0:22:35.16,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Never think !
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.33,0:22:37.04,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Keep pushing on !
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.29,0:22:44.13,EDEN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}We can find our promised land
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.47,0:21:34.27,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}离乡远行 已经历漫长时光
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.31,0:21:40.52,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}年年日日 漂泊在星河八荒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.53,0:21:43.99,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我欲去往何处
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.57,0:21:47.07,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我在追寻何物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.41,0:21:52.16,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}寒冷 迷茫 在黑暗中流浪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.25,0:21:59.04,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}但我心中仍存一线希望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.83,0:22:04.55,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}无论风雨 始终追寻梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.59,0:22:08.68,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}总有一天 我们将横越苍茫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.89,0:22:12.14,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}无所畏惧 展翼翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.31,0:22:16.94,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}我们许下誓言 绝不退让
